nodes.text: Narask was a male Trandoshan, who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.

Narask worked as a bounty hunter and was a regular patron of the Space Monkey Café, a bar that was located on the planet Cularin. He was an associate of the Human Selima DeWitt and when she went missing, the heroes of Cularin, who had been hired to find her, approached Narask in the Café an asked him some questions about her.
Like many members of his species, Narask detested Wookiees.
